sources.description:
Mega Piranha - A genetically modified breed of Piranha, which has grown to giant proportions, escapes into the river, killing everything in its path. Now, at the peak of tourist season, it is headed towards Florida.
2010. Stars: Paul Logan, Tiffany, Barry Williams

metadata.Plot: Mega Piranha (also known as Megapiranha) is a 2010 science fiction disaster film produced by The Asylum. It was directed by Eric Forsberg and stars Tiffany, Paul Logan and Barry Williams. In the tradition of The Asylum's catalog, this film is a mockbuster of Piranha 3-D.
